---
title: Chicken, Bacon and Corn Chowder with Green Onions
description: We've got a chowder that is made for winter and calling your name! Chicken and corn make a hearty duo in this big bowl of goodness and  a touch of jalapeños is just what you need to warm up. Time to get cozy!
